{"tid":473264,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗仔入六粒真勁揪","createTime":"2017-11-19T05:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T12:01:02.000Z","uid":77132,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"48d78fd702f054aefe7ecb2988178cfc647eaa70","tid":473264,"uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:31:04.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里前鋒基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗、右）好波就係人都知，唔知踢波呢回事，天份係咪都有得遺傳㗎呢？話說C朗嘅七歲囝囝Cristiano Jr.（左）日前喺一場學校嘅比賽大發神威，包辦球隊八個入波裏面嘅其中六球，在場睇波嘅老竇梗係勁開心喇。有位世界級球星喺現場睇波，在場嘅家長同小朋友又點會唔知吖，於是C朗完場後就變咗流動佈景板咁，仲滿場飛周圍咁同一班小朋友影相留念㖭。<br />\n<br />\n個仔入波仲勁過老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c76b2b6670a9251cc9addc299c9c28ce947cef","tid":473264,"uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8b9fab9301c83dc7dd2651fe6988acde68e4e0","tid":473264,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"阿朗今年咁嘅狀態<br />\n都唔知入唔入到六粒"},{"pid":"5f7700fda8b19ebca30dd0151d3a24ba0ffa6355","tid":473264,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿朗今年咁嘅狀態<br />\n都唔知入唔入到六粒</blockquote><br />\n仔 182%<br />\n老豆 1.82%"},{"pid":"2cbd0e992d458c8e58bf4a5abc9d9a68b6c21389","tid":473264,"uid":143284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"靈魂同個仔交換左 阿LEE真人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cea2dfe03d7bf7bd4e66b3e6451d03281edc6e","tid":473264,"uid":23385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T07:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>阿朗今年咁嘅狀態<br />\n都唔知入唔入到六粒</blockquote><br />\n仔 182%<br />\n老豆 1.82%</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"